body:
Could you please leave this open? If it's not clear that the problem is only `bazel` then I suggest keeping the issue open on both repos.

If I `git checkout master` then I can get pass the Java exception state but would get into another issue (already reported by someone else [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/119))
